WEBVTT

00:00:28.988 --> 00:00:31.306
Joe believed the patients' claims.

00:00:32.120 --> 00:00:35.634
But when he reported
these complaints to the FDA,

00:00:35.658 --> 00:00:40.088
officials there argued,
"It was probably psychosomatic.

00:00:40.112 --> 00:00:44.480
Patients are upset by pills
that look different from their old ones."

00:00:45.783 --> 00:00:47.587
Joe didn't buy it.

00:00:47.611 --> 00:00:50.976
He wanted someone
with investigative firepower

00:00:51.000 --> 00:00:52.555
to dig into this,

00:00:52.579 --> 00:00:55.042
and since I was
an investigative journalist,

00:00:55.066 --> 00:00:56.455
he called me.

